videos.headline: Army ties the game up
videos.description: Army running back Connor Slomka punches in 1-yard touchdown to tie the game at 7-7.

videos.headline: Murray throws his second TD of the game
videos.description: Kyler Murray connects with CeeDee Lamb for an 11-yard score.

videos.headline: Army scores off QB option
videos.description: Army's Kell Hopkins Jr. keep it himself and runs in 5-yard score.

videos.headline: Murray shows off his unreal speed
videos.description: Oklahoma's Kyler Murray runs through Army's defense for a 33-yard score to take a 21-14 lead.

videos.headline: Army evens score with 3-yard TD
videos.description: Andy Davidson rushes up the middle for a 3-yard touchdown to tie the game up at 21-21.

videos.headline: Sooners gets stuffed at goal line, turn ball over on downs
videos.description: Oklahoma's Trey Sermon can't find his way into the end zone on 4th and goal and the Sooners lose the ball.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's defense forces crucial turnover
videos.description: Sooner linebacker Kenneth Mann picks off a deflected Army pass late in the 4th quarter.

videos.headline: Oklahoma misses game-winning FG as time expires
videos.description: Oklahoma kicker Austin Seibert misses a 33-yard, game-winning field goal with 2 seconds left and sends the game to overtime.

videos.headline: Sooners strike first in OT
videos.description: Kyler Murray and CeeDee Lamb connect for a 10-yard score to give Oklahoma a 28-21 lead over Army.

videos.headline: Oklahoma secures win with OT INT
videos.description: Fred Cooper intercepts the pass on the two-yard line and secures an overtime win for Oklahoma vs. Army.

videos.headline: Murray finds his TE wide open in the end zone
videos.description: Sooners' Kyler Murray tosses it to Carson Meier for an 11-yard touchdown.
